One large flaw in the scheme to make PoS supportive of 2+ raiding parties... Sirran. Only one Sirran can be up at any time and he is your way to keys. So if the people on isle 2 kill the Imp boss and the poeople on isle 7 just whacked thmeseleves a Sister...someone is fubared and bad. And you cannot 'work' this out all the time. There are key carrying mobs that you can only kill after the sister is dead. So you have to have someone hailing Sirran to keep him spawned for a good long while. You do the same thing on isle 3 and on isle 5 as well. /shrug. It just won't work.<br>
